*CO Certified Organic

settings.text:
HOW TO USE THE DARK SPOT TREATMENT DUO

  • Step 1: Wash away impurities+ even skin tone with BODY REFRESHER Glycolic Cleanser. Apply a small amount to dry skin with fingertips. Massage thoroughly into skin using a circular motion. Add water and work through again. Rinse well with lukewarm water. For best results, use once daily at nighttime.
  • Step 2: Hydrate + exfoliate with BODY SMOOTHER Glycolic Lotion. Apply a generous layer focusing on areas with dark spots. Massage into skin using a circular motion until absorbed into skin. For best results, use once daily at nighttime.


    PRO TIP: Add a body massage with dark spot treatment duo into your routine on these areas at least once a week.  Hold the Gua Sha tool at a flat angle and use pressure on the skin as you apply long, lifted strokes upward and outward to activate lymphatic drainage. Continue these motions for 3-4 minutes.
